## FZF
Search History|Ctrl-R|R for reverse
Search and insert file|Ctrl-T
Cd into directory|Alt-C
Search Processes|Ctrl-P|P for process
Kill process|Ctrl-Alt-P
Search Variables|Ctrl-Alt-Shift-V|V for variable
Jump to mark|Ctrl-E|E for explore

## FZF search syntax
'wild|exact-match
'wild'|exact-boundary-match
^music|prefix-exact-match
.mp3$|suffix-exact-match
!fire|inverse-exact-match
!^music|inverse-prefix-exact-match
!.mp3$|inverse-suffix-exact-match
